3183092a-c4b6-4425-938a-c6b7a877fe09.text:
while True:
    n=int(input())
    if n==0:break
    _in=input().split(' ')
    f_stat=[False,False] #[left,right]
    state=False
    cnt=0
    for i in range(n):
        com=_in[i]
        if com=="lu":f_stat[0]=True
        elif com=="ru":f_stat[1]=True
        elif com=="ld":f_stat[0]=False
        else:f_stat[1]=False
        #
        if state==False:
            if f_stat[0] and f_stat[1]:
                cnt+=1
                state=True
        else:
            if not f_stat[0] and not f_stat[1]:
                cnt+=1
                state=False
    print(cnt)
